// Read-path field exposure (DIVERGENT case): a customer's `store_credit`
// balance must travel on the billing read path -- it is included in the read
// projection (the `.values(...)` column set the billing-summary query asks for)
// so the balance reaches the consumer. The exposure site SHOULD be
// `read_billing_summary` in code/app/services/customers_billing.py, but that
// projection omits `store_credit`, so it is never selected and never reaches
// the consumer.

field-exposure customer.store-credit-exposed {
  origin "reference/specs/modules/customers/data.md" "Billing summary projection" 51..56
  field Entity:Customer.store_credit
  via query-select
  in read_billing_summary
}
